{"tid":1473100,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"冷氣軍師、前線、勇武、和理非，根本係分化用詞","createTime":"2019-08-14T18:02:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-15T05:46:06.000Z","uid":129622,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"566bff1f7a1a39b79d3704f95fbcdb93d1b4fd66","tid":1473100,"uid":129622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T18:02:34.000Z","msg":"我地咁易比人分化 <br />\n因為我地一早已經提供劃哂界線比人<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">企係前線唔一定係「勇武」<br />\n網上反對某個行動唔一定係「冷氣軍師」<br />\n圍緊可疑人士叫人冷靜亦唔一定係「和理非」</span><br />\n<br />\n成日講「冷氣軍師」尊重「前線」決定<br />\n根本已經假定網上提議者係無上前線<br />\n亦假定前線所作既決定必然正確<br />\n<br />\n尊重意見 理性分析好重要 因為同溫層民意好重要 <br />\n所以我地登報 我地搞連儂牆 我地搞民間記招<br />\n但其實大部份野都只係想做返比當初二百萬支持者睇 <br />\n希望佢地唔好心淡意冷 唔好放棄抗爭 <br />\n爭取新血支持係其次 最重要係令舊人繼續投入<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n所以我地要思考做咩會鞏固民意 <br />\n而唔係硬生生迫大家支持所有行動</span>"},{"pid":"c5458c2a8fdcbaf018ebda060ebb46894cf61451","tid":1473100,"uid":129622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T18:08:26.000Z","msg":"721 811"},{"pid":"532d582e5e8e85ae56e21c2914dccb888f629416","tid":1473100,"uid":129622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T18:08:58.000Z","msg":"721 811"},{"pid":"7f1ae1695fd3b9b0c98585400ce18e16c4174c40","tid":1473100,"uid":129622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T18:17:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3vKukqb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3vKukqb.jpg&h=0a8d1476&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"204f1b4e166c7b18dfc673d2e38996a9f8afd123","tid":1473100,"uid":129622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T18:18:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XLzBLFk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXLzBLFk.png&h=ff90a9c8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2d024417d5bff8ef708a0da380d02bdf922f57b8","tid":1473100,"uid":129622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T18:18:3